{ A centralized knight is a powerful weapon. It supports the g4-square, can occupy the g6-square, and can even deliver a check on f3. }
11. Bg5 Rg6 12. Qh4 Nf3+ 13. gxf3 h6
{ Gaining a piece back. White's king is exposed. } 14. f4 hxg5 15. fxg5 Nh5
{ Threatening to take on g5 on the next move. Black has a dangerous attack! } *

