12... Rb8 13. g4 { The most aggressive continuation for White. } 13... Nxd4 14.
Bxd4
{ Black exchanges a piece and grabs more space with e6-e5, but this also activates White's pieces. }
14... e5 15. fxe5 dxe5 16. Ba7
