Bc4 { Threatening to play e4-e5. } 7... e6 8. O-O Be7 9. Bg5 O-O
{ In this line, White spent two moves on the light-squared bishop and that's why the initiative slowly went away. As for Black, their development is almost done and they may start to exploit their healthy extra pawn. }
